@startuml
title 미핏 - InterviewRecording 상태 머신 (영상 처리 파이프라인)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
  ArrowColor #555555
  FontSize 11
}
skinparam state<<terminal>> {
  BackgroundColor #C8E6C9
  BorderColor #2E7D32
}
skinparam state<<errstate>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFCDD2
  BorderColor #C62828
}
skinparam state<<process>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
  BorderColor #FBC02D
}

[*] --> UPLOADING : POST /recordings/initiate/

state UPLOADING
UPLOADING : MediaRecorder API 청크 수집
UPLOADING : presign-part / parts / complete
UPLOADING : 지수 백오프 재시도

state UPLOAD_COMPLETED <<process>>
UPLOAD_COMPLETED : original_video_key 저장
UPLOAD_COMPLETED : S3 ObjectCreated 이벤트 발행
UPLOAD_COMPLETED : SNS Fan-out → SQS 3 큐

state PROCESSING <<process>>
PROCESSING : Lambda 4 종 병렬 처리
PROCESSING : - video-converter (.mp4)
PROCESSING : - frame-extractor (.jpg)
PROCESSING : - audio-extractor (.wav + 16kHz)
PROCESSING : 후속:
PROCESSING : - face-analyzer (SQS face-analyzer-queue 트리거)
PROCESSING : - analysis-stt Worker

state COMPLETED <<terminal>>
COMPLETED : scaled_video_key 저장
COMPLETED : frame_prefix 저장
COMPLETED : audio_key + scaled_audio_key 저장
COMPLETED : face_analysis_result 저장
COMPLETED : transcript_status = COMPLETED

state FAILED <<errstate>>
FAILED : 청크 업로드 실패 또는
FAILED : Lambda DLQ 진입
FAILED : 운영자 검토 후 재처리

UPLOADING --> UPLOAD_COMPLETED : 모든 청크 + complete()
UPLOADING --> FAILED : 업로드 실패 (재시도 한도)
UPLOAD_COMPLETED --> PROCESSING : SQS step-complete\n(sqs-celery-worker polling)
PROCESSING --> COMPLETED : 모든 단계 완료
PROCESSING --> FAILED : Lambda 실패 (DLQ)

COMPLETED --> [*]

footer MeFit - backend/webapp/interviews/ + analysis-video/ + face-analyzer/
@enduml
